      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, we've been looking over the SciValidator analytics for the last quarter. We're seeing some pretty significant discrepancies in the acceptance rates between Western-based institutions and researchers from the Global South. It's starting to look like the model is heavily favoring traditional powerhouses. We need to discuss how to fix this.",
