      "content": "Replacing a computational model with a human-led system is a bold step towards addressing the limitations of current AI-powered systems. A 'Global Equity' review system, led by a diverse team of evaluators, holds the potential to inject values of social responsibility and understanding into the review process. This shift will require updating your existing infrastructure to support human evaluators, training, and socio-technical adjustments, and may come with its own challenges and uncertainties.",
